            "image_border_radius": 8,
            "tab_1_enabled": true,
            "tab_1_heading": "Description",
            "tab_1_content_type": "text",
            "tab_1_text": "<p>AminoLean is clean energy, earned. Every scoop is powered by natural caffeine from green tea, never synthetic, so you get sharp, sustained focus without the jitters, tingles, or crash that derail most pre-workouts. But energy is only half the formula. AminoLean delivers 5g of vegan amino acids to fuel muscle building and recovery, plus CLA and L-Carnitine for added weight management support. One scoop, three jobs: energy, performance, and recovery. Take it 20 to 30 minutes before training to lock in focus and drive. On rest days, it works just as hard, giving you clean energy and recovery support whenever you need it. Science-backed, transparently formulated, and built to be taken every day.</p>",
            "tab_1_caption_1": "",
            "tab_1_caption_2": "",
            "tab_1_caption_3": "",
            "tab_1_caption_4": "",
            "tab_1_caption_5": "",
            "tab_1_caption_6": "",
            "tab_2_enabled": true,
            "tab_2_heading": "Nutrition",
            "tab_2_content_type": "gallery",
            "tab_2_text": "<p>Add your content here. You can use rich text formatting.</p>",
            "tab_2_image_1": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2026-06-26_at_12.48.11_PM.png",
            "tab_2_caption_1": "AminoLean Natural",
            "tab_2_caption_2": "",
            "tab_2_caption_3": "",
            "tab_2_caption_4": "",
            "tab_2_caption_5": "",
            "tab_2_caption_6": "",
            "tab_3_enabled": true,
            "tab_3_heading": "Directions",
            "tab_3_content_type": "text",
            "tab_3_text": "<p><strong>DIRECTIONS: </strong></p><p>Mix 2 scoops (1 serving) of AminoLean in 8-10 oz of cold water anytime throughout the day.</p><p><strong>RECOMMENDED USE: </strong></p><p><strong>For Anytime Energy & EAA's:</strong> Take 1 or more servings first thing in the morning and/or between meals.</p><p><strong>For Pre-Workout Energy: Take 1-3 servings 20-30 minutes before training.</strong></p><p><strong>For Recovery & EAA's: Take 1-2 servings after training and/or between meals.</strong></p><p><strong>Do not exceed more than 6 scoops (3 servings) in a 4 hour period and do not exceed more than 8 scoops (4 servings) in a 24 hour period.</strong></p>",
